  Arts &amp; Athletics  
	 
	
    					 
			 
				 
					 Arts 
					  Claire Trevor School of the Arts is UCI's center for innovative, creative engagement in art in all of its facets: production, critique, appreciation and development.  
					    
		
    				
    		
	
	
    		
		
	
			
				  Learn  more about the Claire Trevor School of the Arts   
					    
		
    					
    		
	
	
    		
		
	
			
