  Alumni &amp; Giving  
	 
	
    					 
			 
				 
					 Alumni 
					  Founded in 1968, the UCI Alumni Association offers an enriching and supportive hub for graduates, fosters lifelong Anteater pride and welcomes non-alumni community participation.  
					    
		
    				
    		
	
	
    		
		
	
			
				  Learn  more about the UCI Alumni Association   
					    
		
    				
    		
	
	
    		
		
	
			
				  Join  the UCI Alumni Association   
						 
			 
		 
	
	
    					 
			 
				 
					 Giving 
					 On Wednesday, April 12, UCI will participate in our inaugural Giving Day campaign. Giving Day is an exciting, 24-hour online fundraising campaign supporting your area of interest at UCI. 
					    
		
    				
    		
	
	
    		
		
	
			
